---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Acerca De // Nosotros" description="Conoce a la comunidad detrás de H4ck.cl. Un colectivo de aprendizaje e investigación comprometido con compartir materiales de ciberseguridad.">

    <!-- ===== HERO SECTION ===== -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden border-b border-white/5">
        <!-- Background Layer -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-hacker-red/5 via-hacker-black to-hacker-black"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-30"></div>
            <!-- Animated Scanline -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden">
                <div class="w-full h-[2px] bg-hacker-red/5 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(255,0,0,0.5)] animate-scanline"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- Floating elements -->
            <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 text-hacker-red/5 font-mono text-[120px] font-black leading-none select-none pointer-events-none hidden lg:block">
                //
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 text-hacker-red/5 font-mono text-[100px] font-black leading-none select-none pointer-events-none hidden lg:block">
                &lt;/&gt;
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 py-24">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8">
                <!-- Tag Badge -->
                <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-3 px-4 py-1.5 bg-hacker-red/10 border border-hacker-red/30 rounded text-hacker-red font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
                    <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-hacker-red opacity-75"></span>
                        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-hacker-red"></span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="font-bold">About_Us // Operación_Transparencia</span>
                </div>

                <!-- Main Title with Glitch -->
                <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white leading-[0.95] tracking-tighter uppercase glitch-title" data-text="ACERCA_DE">
                    ACERCA_DE
                </h1>

                <!-- Subtitle -->
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
                    Somos una comunidad y colectivo de aprendizaje e investigación dedicados a documentar y compartir materiales sobre ciberseguridad.
                </p>

                <!-- Scroll indicator -->
                <div class="pt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-zinc-600">
                    <span class="text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">Scroll_Down</span>
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-double-down text-hacker-red animate-bounce"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative UI elements -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-12 right-12 hidden lg:flex flex-col items-end gap-2 opacity-20 font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-500">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2">NODE_STATUS: [ACTIVE] <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-hacker-red/50"></div></span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2">CLEARANCE: [LEVEL_5] <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-zinc-800"></div></span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2">PROTOCOL: [SECURE] <i class="bi bi-shield-check text-hacker-red"></i></span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== MISIÓN SECTION ===== -->
    <section class="py-32 border-b border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Subtle BG glow -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-[150px] rounded-full"></div>
        
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-hacker-red uppercase tracking-[0.5em] block mb-4">Directive_01</span>
                        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter uppercase mb-6">NUESTRA_MISIÓN</h2>
                        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-hacker-red"></div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
                        <strong class="text-white">H4ck.cl</strong> nació de la necesidad de crear un espacio donde la comunidad hispanohablante de ciberseguridad pueda acceder a material técnico y de investigación, de forma colaborativa.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
                        Creemos firmemente que el aprendizaje sobre seguridad informática debe ser libre y accesible. Por eso, nos dedicamos a compartir apuntes, recursos y análisis en español.
                    </p>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-hacker-red"></i>
                            <span>Open_Source</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-hacker-red"></i>
                            <span>Community_Driven</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-hacker-red"></i>
                            <span>100%_Español</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Terminal Visual -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="bg-hacker-dark border border-white/10 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-hacker-red/5">
                        <!-- Terminal Header -->
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-hacker-black border-b border-white/5">
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-hacker-red/60"></div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/30"></div>
                            <span class="ml-4 font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-widest">root@h4ck_cl:~</span>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Terminal Body -->
                        <div class="p-6 font-mono text-sm space-y-3">
                            <div class="text-zinc-600"><span class="text-hacker-red">$</span> cat /etc/mission.conf</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-400 pl-4 border-l-2 border-hacker-red/30 space-y-2 py-2">
                                <div><span class="text-zinc-600">[CORE]</span></div>
                                <div>nombre = <span class="text-hacker-red">"H4ck.cl"</span></div>
                                <div>tipo = <span class="text-hacker-red">"Comunidad de Aprendizaje"</span></div>
                                <div>idioma = <span class="text-hacker-red">"es-CL"</span></div>
                                <div>licencia = <span class="text-hacker-red">"Open Knowledge"</span></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600"><span class="text-hacker-red">$</span> uptime</div>
                            <div class="text-green-400/80">Activo desde 2026 // 100% operativo</div>
                            <div class="text-zinc-600 animate-pulse"><span class="text-hacker-red">$</span> <span class="border-r-2 border-hacker-red">_</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Glow behind terminal -->
                    <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-3xl rounded-3xl -z-10"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== QUÉ HACEMOS SECTION ===== -->
    <section class="py-32 border-b border-white/5 relative">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-20">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-hacker-red uppercase tracking-[0.5em] block mb-4">Operations_Overview</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter uppercase mb-6">QUÉ_HACEMOS</h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light text-lg">Áreas de operación y líneas de investigación activas en nuestra plataforma.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div class="group relative bg-hacker-dark border border-white/5 rounded p-10 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-hacker-red/30 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-3xl rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded bg-hacker-black border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-hacker-red/40 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,0,0,0.15)] transition-all">
                            <i class="bi bi-shield-lock text-3xl text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-hacker-red transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Análisis de Amenazas</h3>
                        <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Investigación profunda de malware, ransomware, APTs y vectores de ataque emergentes. Reportes detallados con indicadores de compromiso (IOCs).</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-700 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
                            <span>Operativo</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div class="group relative bg-hacker-dark border border-white/5 rounded p-10 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-hacker-red/30 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-3xl rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded bg-hacker-black border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-hacker-red/40 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,0,0,0.15)] transition-all">
                            <i class="bi bi-terminal text-3xl text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-hacker-red transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Pentesting & Red Team</h3>
                        <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Guías prácticas de hacking ético, técnicas de explotación, escalada de privilegios y bypass de defensas. Metodologías reales de campo.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-700 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
                            <span>Operativo</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <div class="group relative bg-hacker-dark border border-white/5 rounded p-10 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-hacker-red/30 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-3xl rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded bg-hacker-black border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-hacker-red/40 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,0,0,0.15)] transition-all">
                            <i class="bi bi-flag text-3xl text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-hacker-red transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Writeups de CTF</h3>
                        <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Soluciones detalladas de desafíos Capture The Flag de plataformas como HackTheBox, TryHackMe, PortSwigger Labs y competencias internacionales.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-700 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
                            <span>Operativo</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 4 -->
                <div class="group relative bg-hacker-dark border border-white/5 rounded p-10 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-hacker-red/30 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-3xl rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded bg-hacker-black border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-hacker-red/40 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,0,0,0.15)] transition-all">
                            <i class="bi bi-book text-3xl text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-hacker-red transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Certificaciones</h3>
                        <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Recursos, guías de estudio y experiencias reales sobre certificaciones como OSCP, CEH, eJPT, CPTS y más del ecosistema de seguridad ofensiva.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-700 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
                            <span>Operativo</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 5 -->
                <div class="group relative bg-hacker-dark border border-white/5 rounded p-10 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-hacker-red/30 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-3xl rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded bg-hacker-black border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-hacker-red/40 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,0,0,0.15)] transition-all">
                            <i class="bi bi-search text-3xl text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-hacker-red transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">OSINT & Forensics</h3>
                        <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Técnicas de inteligencia de fuentes abiertas, análisis forense digital, recuperación de datos y rastreo de actores maliciosos en la red.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-700 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
                            <span>Operativo</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 6 -->
                <div class="group relative bg-hacker-dark border border-white/5 rounded p-10 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-hacker-red/30 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-3xl rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded bg-hacker-black border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-hacker-red/40 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,0,0,0.15)] transition-all">
                            <i class="bi bi-braces text-3xl text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-hacker-red transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Programación & Dev</h3>
                        <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Desarrollo de herramientas de seguridad, scripting ofensivo en Python, automatización de escaneos y creación de exploits personalizados.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-700 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
                            <span>Operativo</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== VALORES SECTION ===== -->
    <section class="py-32 border-b border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-hacker-red/5 blur-[150px] rounded-full"></div>
        
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-20">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-hacker-red uppercase tracking-[0.5em] block mb-4">Core_Values</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter uppercase mb-6">PRINCIPIOS_FUNDAMENTALES</h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light text-lg">Los pilares que guían cada operación y cada decisión dentro de nuestra comunidad.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <!-- Value 1 -->
                <div class="bg-hacker-black p-12 space-y-4 group hover:bg-hacker-dark transition-colors">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="text-4xl font-black text-hacker-red/20 font-mono group-hover:text-hacker-red/40 transition-colors">01</span>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Ética Ante Todo</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-14">Promovemos el uso responsable y ético de las habilidades de seguridad. Todo nuestro contenido está orientado al aprendizaje defensivo y la mejora de la postura de seguridad.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Value 2 -->
                <div class="bg-hacker-black p-12 space-y-4 group hover:bg-hacker-dark transition-colors">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="text-4xl font-black text-hacker-red/20 font-mono group-hover:text-hacker-red/40 transition-colors">02</span>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Conocimiento Libre</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-14">La información de seguridad no debe estar detrás de paywalls. Creemos en la democratización del conocimiento técnico para fortalecer la comunidad.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Value 3 -->
                <div class="bg-hacker-black p-12 space-y-4 group hover:bg-hacker-dark transition-colors">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="text-4xl font-black text-hacker-red/20 font-mono group-hover:text-hacker-red/40 transition-colors">03</span>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Rigor Técnico</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-14">Cada publicación pasa por un proceso de revisión técnica. No publicamos rumores ni teorías sin fundamento; solo datos verificables y reproducibles.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Value 4 -->
                <div class="bg-hacker-black p-12 space-y-4 group hover:bg-hacker-dark transition-colors">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="text-4xl font-black text-hacker-red/20 font-mono group-hover:text-hacker-red/40 transition-colors">04</span>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Comunidad Primero</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-14">H4ck.cl es de la comunidad para la comunidad. Cualquier persona puede compartir sus investigaciones y materiales con nosotros a través de la plataforma.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== CTA SECTION ===== -->
    <section class="py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-hacker-red/5 to-transparent"></div>
        
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-10">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-1 border border-hacker-red/20 bg-hacker-red/5 rounded">
                    <i class="bi bi-broadcast text-hacker-red text-sm"></i>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-hacker-red uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">Recruitment_Active</span>
                </div>

                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter uppercase">ÚNETE AL_COLECTIVO</h2>

                <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    ¿Quieres ser parte de nuestro espacio de aprendizaje? ¿Deseas compartir tus apuntes, investigaciones o herramientas? H4ck.cl es un espacio abierto para investigadores y curiosos.
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 pt-4">
                    <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}generator`} class="px-8 py-4 bg-hacker-red text-white font-mono text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transition-all hover:bg-hacker-red-dim shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,0,0,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,0,0,0.5)] flex items-center space-x-3 no-underline">
                        <span>CREAR_REPORTE</span>
                        <i class="bi bi-pencil-square"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex items-center space-x-3 px-8 py-4 bg-hacker-dark border border-white/10 text-white font-mono text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:border-hacker-red/50 hover:bg-hacker-red/5 transition-all no-underline">
                        <i class="bi bi-github text-lg"></i>
                        <span>GITHUB</span>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Stats footer -->
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-12 pt-16 border-t border-white/5">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <span class="text-3xl font-black text-hacker-red">100%</span>
                        <span class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Gratuito</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-12 bg-white/10"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <span class="text-3xl font-black text-hacker-red">ES</span>
                        <span class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">En_Español</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-12 bg-white/10"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <span class="text-3xl font-black text-hacker-red">24/7</span>
                        <span class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Activo</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-12 bg-white/10"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <span class="text-3xl font-black text-hacker-red">∞</span>
                        <span class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Open_Source</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>

<style>

    .grid-bg {
        background-image: 
            linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 60px 60px;
    }
    
    @keyframes scanline {
        0% { transform: translateY(-100vh); }
        100% { transform: translateY(100vh); }
    }
    
    .animate-scanline {
        animation: scanline 8s linear infinite;
    }
</style>
